sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User/CodeFlare SDK
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant MCAD as MCAD Controller<br/>In-process
    participant InstaScale as InstaScale Controller<br/>In-process (Optional)
    participant MachineAPI as Machine API<br/>MachineSets
    participant Prometheus as Prometheus<br/>8080/TCP HTTP

    Note over User,K8sAPI: Flow 1: AppWrapper Submission and Scheduling

    User->>K8sAPI: Create AppWrapper CR<br/>Auth: User credentials
    K8sAPI-->>MCAD: Watch Event (AppWrapper)
    MCAD->>K8sAPI: Validate quotas<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>MCAD: Quota check result
    MCAD->>MCAD: Queue job, check priorities
    MCAD->>K8sAPI: Create wrapped resources<br/>(Pods, Jobs, RayClusters)<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>MCAD: Resources created

    Note over MCAD,MachineAPI: Flow 2: InstaScale Auto-Scaling (OpenShift only)

    MCAD->>K8sAPI: Update AppWrapper status<br/>(unmet resources)<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>InstaScale: Watch Event (AppWrapper)
    InstaScale->>InstaScale: Calculate required nodes
    InstaScale->>K8sAPI: Create/Scale MachineSets<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI->>MachineAPI: Provision new machines
    MachineAPI-->>K8sAPI: New nodes join cluster
    K8sAPI-->>MCAD: Node availability event
    MCAD->>K8sAPI: Schedule AppWrapper workload<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token

    Note over Prometheus,MCAD: Flow 3: Metrics Collection

    Prometheus->>MCAD: GET /metrics<br/>8080/TCP HTTP<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    MCAD-->>Prometheus: Queue metrics, AppWrapper counts,<br/>controller runtime metrics
